- `generate_artistic_name()` creates adjective-noun names from fixed word lists.
- Default identity persistence path is `~/.promptclaw/identity.json`.
- Daemon startup now calls `bootstrap_identity()` before `FirstBootAnnouncer`, so first-boot creation is tied into poll startup.

